reviewText: ok... fun to see
I love how it is nonstick, but the pan itself is so flimsy! It makes it hard to work with. Over all a good product though.

I love stand up comedy, so anybody giving a full on performance like Larry the Cable Guy does, is alright by me. I like some of his material, but not all of it. This is definitely worth watching/hearing, although it isn't one that I return to again and again.
I laughed so much. Larry the cable guy is hilarious. He is one funny comedian these days with out  the filthy language. I highly recommend this tape.
This is a great dvd if your not too much of a prude. It is sooo funny I have watched it so many times and laughed as hard as the first time.

Either you like Larry's bathroom humor or you do not.  I do.  If you like it, you will enjoy this standup comedy show... It's hard to believe ANYONE could listen to this without laughing.  I've seen Larry do slightly better, but this is really good.
Great standup

I absolutely love him. He is soo funny!  He does not have a vulgar mouth (cussing) like a lot of comedians do.  They all think its hilarous to use the "F" word in their routines, Larry does not.  He's just a good ol boy with a good heart.
hilarious. one of the best comedians out there.
Larry The Cable Guy, is one of the funniest comidians, out there. And, I think this is one of his best shows, that he's done.
